{
  "stem": "12684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this woman who rented it originally, she stayed in the apartment when we moved back in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she had the room where it was always raining, because the roof was broken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we ended up having her stay in our rooms, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it took a long time until I was able to do anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I worked for the English occupational forces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cultural relations.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was for a man called [INAUDIBLE], and who was quite a well-known author, was at this time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, the money was so worthless.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For the money which I made in a month, I could buy for my mother a pound of butter, because she was very frail and very sick.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until I got here, some-- sometime in the '50s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the '50s.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had the opportunity, as-- you know, as everybody was given, that they could leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother had remarried again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] had a friend who lived in New York, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they persuaded me that I should come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them looked at us like [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] green men from the moon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh god, they're back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them in utter disgust that we didn't get killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And some of them were genuinely very happy to see us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Very strange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you like it when somebody tells you oh, you know, the weeds are back again?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, [LAUGHS] what can you say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ignore it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the others, you don't need to see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't even need to have anything to do with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those who were genuinely happy, they're my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
